Titolo: Greg Hastings' Tournament Paintball

Anno: 2004

Descrizione: Greg Hastings' Tournament Paintball (2004) (GHTP) is a first person paintball game released exclusively for the Xbox.  The game gathered a cult following, consistently appearing on the Xbox Live Top 25 list posted by Major Nelson, peaking at the number nine position.  A spin-off, Greg Hastings Tournament Paintball MAX'D, was also released on multiple platforms many months later, with a full sequel released in 2010 for the Wii, PlayStation 3 and Xbox 360.

Genere: First Person Shooter

Valutazione: 63
